          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1712.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain the <strong>tofu</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and chop roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tofu</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>softened mushrooms</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Blitz with a <strong>stick blender</strong> until a rough paste forms – this is your<strong> tofu mix</strong></p>",
