    {
      "instruction": "<p>Roll the <strong>tofu mix</strong> into 10 <span class=\"text-danger\">[20]</span> balls (clean hands are the best way!)</p><p>Add the <strong>tofu balls</strong> to a lightly oiled baking tray</p><p>Brush each <strong>tofu ball</strong> with <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and put the tray in the oven for 25 min or until lightly golden and crisp</p><p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>",
