    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>spring greens</strong> then pat it dry with kitchen paper </p><p>Rip the leaves off the <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> </strong>in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
