    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>wholewheat noodles</strong> to a large bowl, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir for 10 secs to separate the noodles</p><p>Set aside to soak for 4 min</p><p>Drain the <strong>soaked noodles</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
