    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>agave </strong>with 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span><strong> cold water</strong> and cook for 3 min or until the sauce thickens slightly</p><p>Once thickened, transfer to a small bowl – this is your<strong> sticky soy sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
