      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tofu balls</strong> over the <strong>vegetable noodle stir-fry </strong>and drizzle over the <strong>sticky soy sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds </strong>and <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
